data.description: Come one, come all to this new 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom split foyer listing located in the Laquey School District.  This home has all new flooring throughout!  Living room, kitchen, dining space all have laminate wood flooring. Kitchen features a pantry, stainless steel stove & dishwasher, and white refrigerator. Located on the main level is the master bedroom suite, two guest bedrooms, and a full guest bathroom.  Downstairs you'll find another bedroom, bathroom, bonus office, and laundry room.  All bedrooms have new carpeting!  Other great features include a two car garage, front and back deck, flat yard!  Call to schedule your showing before this home is gone!
